<div align="center">

# 🎓📱 CollegeSurfer — All-in-One College Management Android App

An Android app that simplifies and automates key college operations — from hostels to libraries, assignments to lost-and-found. Built with ❤️ using Java, XML, and Firebase.

![Platform](https://img.shields.io/badge/platform-Android-green?logo=android)
![Tech](https://img.shields.io/badge/Built_with-Java_&_Firebase-blue?logo=java)
![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Active-brightgreen)

</div>

---

## 📲 Features Overview

| ✨ Module | ⚡ Description |
|----------|----------------|
| 🏨 **Hostel Management** | Handles hostel admissions, allocations, and status tracking from one screen. |
| 📚 **Library System** | Real-time open/close status, stock information, and notifications. |
| 🛒 **Co-op Store Management** | Same as the library module — but for your college's co-op store! |
| 📑 **Assignments, Attendance & Results** | Faculty can upload all academic updates; students can instantly access them. |
| 📦 **Lost & Found** | Lost something? Post it! Found something? Help return it. |
| 📘 **Book Buy & Sell** | Peer-to-peer platform for students to trade old/new books. |
| 🎉 **Events Feed** | View and get notified about all upcoming college events. |

---

## 🔐 Admin Panel System

Each department has a **dedicated admin interface**, yet everything is **unified in a single app**. Admins log in to their panel and manage

