🛠️ Getting Started

# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/maivyash/CollegeSurfer.git

# Open the project in Android Studio
# Connect your Firebase project
# Sync Gradle and run on emulator or device
✅ Make sure to:

Connect Firebase Authentication and Database in your Firebase console

Update the google-services.json file

Add proper rules to Firebase DB and Storage

